        "text": "Arya Verma\n+91-8957920878| aryaverma888@gmail.com\n| linkedin.com/in/arya-verma| github.com/cout-arya\nEducation\nManipal University JaipurJaipur, Rajasthan\nBachelor of Technology in Computer Science EngineeringExpected May 2027\nDelhi Public SchoolPrayagraj, Uttar Pradesh\nSenior Secondary (Class XII)Graduated 2023\nTechnical Skills\nLanguages: JavaScript, C++, Python, SQL, HTML5, CSS3\nFrontend: React.js, Next.js, Redux, Tailwind CSS, Bootstrap, Material-UI, Responsive Design\nBackend: Node.js, Express.js, RESTful APIs, GraphQL, JWT Authentication, Microservices Architecture\nDatabases: MongoDB, MySQL, PostgreSQL, Redis, FAISS Vector DB, Database Design, Query Optimization\nAI/ML: RAG Systems, Vector Embeddings, OpenAI API, Google Gemini, Prompt Engineering\nDevOps & Tools: Docker, Git, GitHub Actions, CI/CD, Postman, Linux, Render, Vercel\nProblem Solving: Data Structures & Algorithms (150+ LeetCode, 50+ GeeksforGeeks), Dynamic Programming\nProjects\nSpottr — AI-Powered Social Fitness PlatformGitHub— Live\nMERN Stack, RAG, Socket.io, Docker, FAISSOct 2024 – Dec 2024\n•\nArchitected full-stack social media platform for fitness enthusiasts featuring user profiles, social connections, activity\nfeeds, and AI-powered nutrition planning using RAG architecture with FAISS vector database and LangChain\n•\nEngineered geolocation-based social matching algorithm with weighted compatibility scoring to connect users with\nworkout partners based on proximity, fitness levels, and shared goals\n•\nIntegrated real-time social messaging using Socket.io WebSockets enabling instant user communication with\nMongoDB persistence\nTruBalance — Financial Management & Invoicing SystemGitHub— Live\nMERN Stack, JWT, Chart.js, REST APIsAug 2024 – Oct 2024\n•\nBuilt intelligent expense tracking platform with AI-powered insights engine analyzing spending patterns, detecting\nanomalies, and generating personalized budget recommendations using statistical algorithms\n•\nEngineered rule-based AI system for smart transaction categorization across 15+ categories with pattern\nrecognition and financial health scoring\n•\nDesigned systematized invoicing workflow with state management (Draft/Sent/Paid/Overdue), computerized GST\ncalculations, and JWT-secured RESTful APIs\n•\nCreated interactive analytics dashboard with Chart.js displaying AI-generated insights, predictive forecasts, and\ncategory-wise expense breakdowns\nQuizMaster.AI — Real-Time AI Quiz PlatformGitHub\n— Live\nNode.js, Socket.io, OpenAI API, WebSocketsJun 2024 – Aug 2024\n•\nCreated AI-powered quiz platform using GPT-4 API to dynamically generate quizzes from custom topics or\nuploaded PDF documents with automated grading\n•\nImplemented real-time multiplayer architecture using Socket.io with live leaderboards, instant scoring, and\nhost-player session management\n•\nDeveloped anti-cheating system monitoring tab switches and window focus events, with automated result reports\nand performance analytics\nCertifications\nDesign and Analysis of Algorithms — NPTEL\nData Structures and Algorithms Using Java — NPTEL\nObject Oriented Programming Using Java — GeeksforGeeks\nDatabase Programming with SQL — Oracle Academy",
